TextEng: How much are your rooms?
Could I ask you a few questions?

Goodbye.
Just what is going on in Luskan, anyway?
Text: 러스칸에서 도대체 무슨 일이 벌어지고 있는 거죠?

TextEng: Have you heard of any cults in the city?
Text: 이 도시에서 사교에 대해 들은 게 있나요?

TextEng: Is there anywhere I can find work here?
Text: 여기서 일거리를 구할 만한 곳이 있을까요?

TextEng: I need some directions, actually.
What go on in city?
Have you heard of any cults in the city?
Me look for work. What you know?
Me not know way around city. You help?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Is there any correlation between the plague in Neverwinter and the fighting, here?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 네버윈터의 역병과 여기 싸움 사이에 연관이 있나요?

TextEng: Maybe I could ask you something else.
Me want to ask other question.
Where is the nearest temple?
Is there someplace nearby to buy equipment?
Text: 근처에 장비를 살 수 있는 곳이 있나요?

TextEng: Where can I find the Host Tower?
Where close temple?
Need to find store.
Where me find Host Tower?
Who are you?
Who you be?

TextEng: Tell me about the High Captains.
Why doesn't someone put a stop to this?
Text: 왜 아무도 이걸 막지 않는 거죠?

TextEng: Have you heard any rumors?
What start all this? You knows?

Tell me about Baram.
Tell me about Kurth.
You tell me stuff 'bout Baram.
You tell me stuff 'bout Kurth.

Can you think of anyone who might know more?
Text: 더 많이 알 만한 사람 생각나는 사람 있어요?

TextEng: What you says? Necromancers?
You knows someone, maybe, who tell more?
Text: 더 말해 줄 사람, 혹시 알아?
